Description:
    Generate the CRUD files for a model in the CMS

Example:
    rails generate crud ModelSingularName

    This will create:
        app/views/cms/#{ModelSingularName}/index.html.slim
        app/views/cms/#{ModelSingularName}/edit.html.slim
        app/views/cms/#{ModelSingularName}/show.html.slim
        app/views/cms/#{ModelSingularName}/new.html.slim
        app/views/cms/#{ModelSingularName}/_form.html.slim
        app/controllers/cms/#{ModelSingularName}_controller.rb

    This will edit these files:
        app/config.routes.rb
